sources.description: From IMDb: Seven episodes light-heartedly revolving around sexuality and eros with seven funny characters all played by great Nino Manfredi. ----------- Sylva Koscina plays herself in the movie and I like to think that, in fact, she did spend much of her time driving around in a little sports car wearing tiger skin spandex
